  32           * -# WAITS_INST_VDD_GE3600MV_CLK_LT10M         Configuration for main frequency < 10MHz
  33           * -# WAITS_INST_VDD_GE3600MV_CLK_GE10_LT20M    Configuration for main frequency >= 10 and < 20MHz 
